snippet.title: Ittle Dew 2+ Nintendo Switch Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Ittle Dew 2+, the charming “puzzly adventure” for Nintendo Switch, will be available on November 14 at retail and digitally via the Nintendo eShop. Join the sassy adventurer Ittle and her flying fox friend Tippsie as they make friends and enemies on a faraway island loaded with treasure and mysterious secrets!
